main event: A witness in Toledo, Ohio reported seeing a bright blue-green object that was hovering over their car and emitting a humming sound in February 1967.
interesting points: The object was observed for several minutes before descending.
The witness stopped their car and got out to observe the object.
The witness stated they would complete any forms sent to them regarding the sighting.
The report indicates that the information received was not sufficient for a scientific evaluation.
The report is part of Project 10973, a project related to the investigation of unidentified flying objects.
